  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>With its elevated position above the crystalline waters of Lake Gara, the Hotel Villa Del Sogno is one of the most prestigious properties on the Gardone Riviera. The Liberty-style villa boasts unspoiled, verdant acreage and traditional interiors. Unrivaled views of the lake along with antique finishes to the decor and works of art unique to the history of the villa itself make the Hotel Villa Del Sogno the ideal place to stay on the lakeside.  </p>]]></listingDescription>
